SUB_W01_WRLD_BOFO_INITIAL_000_CUT_010_00.text:
I knew it! This is Miyako City in the East Islands!
I can tell because of that tower over there;
it's called Rakusuiro Tower.

SUB_W01_EVAR_BOFO_SANGENIN_SPRING_020_CU.text:
That's only a temporary victory;
I fully expect that man to show
up again and give us trouble.
